title: Six String Samurai - 1957 Drive-In Edition
description:
See the classic cult movie Six String Samurai as you've never seen it before! Lovingly restored from the original black and white print, this film includes all of the trailers, advertisements and public service announcements that accompanied it in its original 1957 theatrical release. Don't miss this chance to have a piece of film history.

From IMDB: In the post-apocalyptic world of 1960s Nevada, a rock 'n' roll samurai takes a young boy under his protection.
